=== FILE: AUTHORS ===
OWNER: GitDigital Products
AUTHOR: RickCreator87

Purpose

Enumerates all individuals and organizations that have contributed to the EGTS project and hold authorship rights.

Definitions

· Author: Any entity that has submitted a change that was merged into the main branch.

Roles & Responsibilities

· GitDigital Products – Maintains the definitive list of authors.
· RickCreator87 – Verifies that each author has signed the CLA.
· Authors have no governance authority unless also designated as owners or maintainers.

Requirements

· Every commit author must appear in this file or in a signed‑off-by trailer.
· Adding a new author requires a pull request approved by any owner.
· Authors must provide a valid email address for project notifications.

Author List (alphabetical)

· GitDigital Products <legal@gitdigital.example>
· RickCreator87 <rick@gitdigital.example>

Governance Alignment

This file supports the contributor recognition policy in GOVERNANCE.md. Missing authorship does not affect intellectual property rights.

